wiki.text:
'Adamyan' (, ) is an Armenian surname. Notable people with the surname include:

*Andranik Adamyan, Armenian football manager *Armen Adamyan (born 1967),
Armenian footballer and manager *Artur Adamyan (born 1992), Russian-Armenian
footballer *Samvel Adamyan, Armenian football manager *Vadym Adamyan (born
1938), Ukrainian mathematician and theoretical physicist
